Evan-Burrows Fontaine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evan-Burrows_Fontaine 0 Evan-Burrows Fontaine (October 3, 1898 – December 27, 1984) was an American Denishawn-trained interpretive dancer and actress whose career suffered after she became entangled in a breach of promise lawsuit with a member of one of America's wealthiest families.
